{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/h1.png?t=1738158411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To unlock the boxes of this escape room game, you have to interact with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. You can find puzzle pieces on the side of the boxes as well. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/1.gif?t=1738158411\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/h2.png?t=1738158411\" />The illusion of holding a real object in total darkness is compelling!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/h3.png?t=1738158411\" />Once you open all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and find a brief history of the discovered invention. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/3.gif?t=1738158411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Think outside of the box to solve all enigmas, it's not always an easy job to escape the rooms! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/h4.png?t=1738158411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/2.gif?t=1738158411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/h5.png?t=1738158411\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play the game with your headphones on to get immersed in this amazing adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/h6.png?t=1738158411\" />Got stuck on some riddle? Tap the bulb button to get a helpful hint! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/h7.png?t=1738158411\" />Available in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>*The game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735790/extras/xslogo2.png?t=1738158411\" />Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of\u00a0 <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Metal Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1735790/7b2e7bec2700b2399d1bf973f043cfb59d268033.jpg"},{"name":"Velvet Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1735790/c7968a978834505aff2c4b11308888fc895a22e7.jpg"},{"name":"Black Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1735790/6bea76b5a0ef72d988ef9cb4a5051f5334aae851.jpg"},{"name":"Pearl Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1735790/5aa8bd1b9cf28de91274cd12be897e8f68e142e5.jpg"},{"name":"Wooden Box","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1735790/858f1bb360c5eb1808e004753af6ae023dbc7f43.jpg"},{"name":"Glass Box","p